room_title: Escape room "The Crazy Cat Lady" by Elusive Escape Rooms in Wisconsin Dells

room_description: Your neighbor, “The Crazy Cat Lady” Ethel Mae, has gone away on vacation. You’re asked to look after her cats while she is gone, but they have other things on their minds. They locked the door on you and you find yourself trapped within her apartment amongst them. Will you make it out with your sanity intact or will you go cat crazy in the process?
